title: Queen Rock Montreal (Colour Corrected Version)
description:
This is the colour corrected version shared and in QueenZone by Nitroboy.

This version is an improvement against the 2007 version released by Queen Productions Ltd. and the 2001 VHS version, which the second has better colour than the first.

Nitroboy tried to make the best version between both releases, trying to emulate the real colour of the recording.

Thanks, obviously, to Nitroboy for share his improvement.
